Solar Power Generation

Solar power generation is a system that can create electricity from sunlight.  Created energy is stored in large batteries to supply electricity to houses regardless of weather.  The system has a social significance in that it can be used as a power source at times of natural disasters.
It is also beneficial because the created energy can be sold to power firms.
