Our Customers 




Who We Are


Edison Power Constructors, Inc. delivers infrastructure construction services in the areas of electric transmission, substation and distribution. Based in Phoenix, Arizona, Edison's focus is to deliver first quality services to customers in the entire North American power market.Edison builds on the existing PLH Group capabilities to perform electric transmission and distribution construction services across North America.   



Edison Power's mission is to complete our projects on time and on budget, while building a long-lasting relationship with all clients involved and to positively engage the local communities in which we work. 
 
















 



 





















































